    public class ConfigurationMap
extends org.eclipse.ui.part.ViewPart
implements ICustomTableHeaderSelectionListener, de.ovgu.featureide.fm.core.base.event.IEventListener
    The ConfigurationMap is an overview of all configurations of a feature project. It shows which features of the current project are used in which configurations.
    Author:
    Paul Maximilian Bittner, Antje Moench
